# Cline Rules - Telegram Group Instagram Loader Bot

## Project Overview

This is a **Telegram bot** that downloads and shares Instagram, Facebook, and YouTube media in Telegram group chats. The bot features a **moderator system** allowing multiple users to manage bot activation in any chat they are a member of.

### Key Features

- 📸 **Instagram/Facebook Media Download** - Download photos and videos from Instagram and Facebook posts
- 📝 **Instagram Captions** - Automatically fetches and includes Instagram post captions with shared media
- 🎵 **YouTube Audio Download** - Download YouTube videos as audio (MP3/M4A) with user confirmation
- 👥 **Moderator System** - Multiple moderators can activate/deactivate the bot in their chats
- 🚪 **Doorman Mode** - Automatically deletes join/leave system messages
- 🔐 **Access Control** - Admin can grant/revoke moderator access
- 📝 **Access Requests** - Users can request moderator access via `/access` command
---

